# Screenshots Folder

Add your screenshots here with the following names:

- home.png          - Home page / Anime Discovery
- ai-search.png     - AI Search conversation
- tier-list.png     - Tier List Creator
- calendar.png      - Seasonal Calendar
- my-list.png       - Personal Anime List
- anime-detail.png  - Anime Detail Page
- profile.png       - User Profile & Stats

Recommended size: 1280x720 or similar 16:9 ratio
